{"tid":1495126,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"新移民綜援婦阿珍 月入一萬七千多元度日 ,社署表示「將會提升該個案綜援金至每月21200元」","createTime":"2019-08-22T02:43:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-22T03:03:19.000Z","uid":143756,"like":18,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"d636c90899f5f4d3ec318f68acc67e7fea3d798b","tid":1495126,"uid":143756,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T02:43:48.000Z","msg":"Link: <a href=\"http://www.newss.ipub.one/show/180677\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.newss.ipub.one%2Fshow%2F180677&d=MOEBQbH5BhSBv0g7AWUGIZsm%2Bn8Fwo%2F6aJUx9arcu0Q%3D&h=ae766911\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.newss.ipub.one/show/180677</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">部分節錄</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n大仔自細對高達充滿興趣，幼子也愛玩電視遊戲。四年前阿珍更獲分配公屋三人單位，領取綜援同時更免租。三母子現時每月獲發一萬七千多元綜援金，而她通常每月撥出二至三千多元給兩子買遊戲機及模型，阿珍更大怨屋企已經沒有空間給放遊戲機及模型，阿珍表示「最近大仔又<span style=\"color: red;\">買了一部PS4電視遊戲機及多種遊戲</span>，又需要付出<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">多達4000多元[</span>/red]的費用，生活很辛苦。」<br />\n<br />\n僅餘一萬多千元怎度過日子？阿珍說，平時會到茶餐廳食午餐，晚飯多數到樓下酒樓食飯。更坦言已經沒有閒錢與兩子去旅行，當記者問到生活也不夠時為何還希望到外國旅行?阿珍即說，[red]<strong><strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">到外國旅行是必需品</span></span></strong></strong></span>，所以已向社工要求協助全數資助兩子暑期到英國遊學，見識世界。<br />\n<br />\n阿珍接受訪問時，<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">穿著並不失時髦</span></span>，她說：「我著嘅所有衫褲，每個星期都會去買衫，這都係新衫，我不覺得有什麼特別，因為著新衫對外觀很重要。」<br />\n<br />\n她說過年前到超市<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">買幾包鮑魚片</span></span>，用來炒菜。<br />\n<br />\n記者問到阿芳會否覺得<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">不出外工作便得到一萬七千元很寫意</span></span>? 阿珍回應：「<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">這是政府欠我們的，我覺得還不足夠</span></span>。」<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">E個咩政府??<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔番工每個月有$21000 我番工尼托 </span></span><br />\n<br />\nbtw <span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">光複香港 時代革命</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a190473f4de45cb8862e8e94bb0dd7462e94a44","tid":1495126,"uid":160102,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T02:44:47.000Z","msg":"屌佢老母臭閪"},{"pid":"d1b709c7820ae06a8fea0bb11e7bea8ec142d9ff","tid":1495126,"uid":23785,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T02:45:25.000Z","msg":"似係Content farm fake news"},{"pid":"a429eda7e89acea2c510b252e716f3cb0feb91fb","tid":1495126,"uid":281926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T02:45:50.000Z","msg":"各位巴打絲打，頂住呀！<br />\n路還很長，記住齊上齊落！<br />\n香港人可攻可守，智勇雙全！<br />\n記住<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>永不分化！不割蓆！不篤灰！</strong></span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\"><strong>It&rsquo;s now or never</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\"><strong>824 機場復活，WE WANT YOU</strong></span></span> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yrRtRqw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyrRtRqw.jpg&h=a938cd9a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wTCkHxb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwTCkHxb.jpg&h=73ff0599&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/00prC5w.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F00prC5w.jpg&h=ccabd632&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WJckHxb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWJckHxb.jpg&h=e84b0cd3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.c